snippet.title: TIME BREAKER - OFFICIAL LAUNCH TRAILER
snippet.description:
TIME BREAKER - OFFICIAL LAUNCH TRAILER

TIME BREAKER is a single player, first person puzzle game mixing puzzle and storyline, created by one-person. 

You play as Judy, she wakes up in a strange facility called « Naera Laboratory ». Everyone is dead, but someone seems to be alive, it’s « Anna » the last scientist alive.

Available now on Steam:  
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1623440/TIME_BREAKER/
